{"tid":2292500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：將會用公帑資助大灣區公司（包括國企）聘請香港青年人","createTime":"2020-11-19T13:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T05:15:17.000Z","uid":137088,"like":1,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"6ecd25cf69b3df5dd728617d3f2840614c45248f","tid":2292500,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:58:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥將於下周三（11月25日）公布新一份《施政報告》，《星島日報》引述消息報道，林鄭月娥將於發表《施政報告》時，宣布大灣區青年就業計劃。報道指，大灣區青年就業計劃，將支援數千香港青年到大灣區城市工作一年，涵蓋的行業包括科技、金融業等，設有年齡限制，每月工資可達1.5萬至2萬元，政府將會提供資助，惟實際細節尚未確定。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，有關計劃將以配對形式運作，騰訊 （00700） 等多家大企業已表示感興趣提供職位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://inews.hket.com/article/2807192/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2807192%2F&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=8c89105d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://inews.hket.com/article/2807192/</a>"},{"pid":"c93f6b71eb04586134dbd64d2f05ba2c46528c0e","tid":2292500,"uid":156652,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U9kDtHB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU9kDtHB.jpg&h=b8fb15e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cadb905f9dbd6dbade3b2c5f7f9f5d4595086474","tid":2292500,"uid":167394,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"50%稅<br />\n回血劍"},{"pid":"316a9aa1bf033b23770b4de2c416a4f09089ef7d","tid":2292500,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:01:12.000Z","msg":"直接係國庫搶錢接濟支那豬"},{"pid":"4190d2c0ca4018c6526fbe097f49d4d6e4f1f29d","tid":2292500,"uid":85116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:03:59.000Z","msg":"比錢人地去請香港人(內地專才)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明搶"},{"pid":"2da8ccc997a2520bd8792117a0f1329146071ce9","tid":2292500,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T16:17:56.0